Package ca.usask.simlab.odeToJava.scheme

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    ARKButcherTableau
    An abstract class that defines a Butcher tableau for a 2-additive Runge-Kutta method.
    ERKButcherTableau
    This class holds information about a single explicit Runge-Kutta scheme in the form of a Butcher tableau.
    ForwardEulerTableau
    A dummy tableau for the forward Euler method.
    IMEXESDIRKButcherTableau
    Class that defines IMEX Butcher tableau with an explicit method as the first tableau and an explicit singly diagonally-implicit Runge-Kutta method as the second tableau, which has the first stage explicit in the tableau.
    Scheme
    An abstract class that defines a method scheme, including the order, coefficients, and any other essential properties.
    StormerVerletTableau
    A dummy tableau for the Stormer-Verlet method of order 2.
